{"title":"hexo+aurora+github+gitalk搭建属于自己的个人博客","uid":"e3447cde20e84ead44a473b80d153b14","slug":"hexo+aurora+github+gitalk搭建属于自己的个人博客","date":"2022-09-24T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-09-25T18:39:39.344Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo+aurora+github+gitalk搭建属于自己的个人博客.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fate-zuolun/blog_img@main/202209251716332.jpg","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>搭建方法主要来自于<a href=\"https://yishuihean.cn/post/hexo-aurora-github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\">依水何安</a>和<a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/zh/\">Aurora官方文档</a></p></blockquote>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>由于上面两个文档讲的很详细，左轮这边就不多加赘述了。这边主要是对一些资源以及遇到的一些问题的重新整合。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"1-node-js的安装及环境配置\"><a href=\"#1-node-js的安装及环境配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.node js的安装及环境配置\"></a>1.node js的安装及环境配置</h2><p>参考<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/zhouyu2017/\">周瑜周</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-安装git\"><a href=\"#2-安装git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装git\"></a>2.安装git</h2><p>参考<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/\">学为所用</a>和<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_37802038\">xxkinger</a></p>\n<p>由于学为所用的博客git版本较低，建议大家可以对照着看</p>\n<p>如果git下载过慢，建议用<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45122120\">Web_阿凯</a>链接中的淘宝镜像解决</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-下载hexo\"><a href=\"#3-下载hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.下载hexo\"></a>3.下载hexo</h2><p>用npm指令时，可能遇到全局安装报错问题，这时候可以参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42287935\">mjzy</a></p>\n<p>安装以上软件，出现错误代码2503问题，可以参照<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/baidu_39212797\">ckm紫韵</a></p>\n<p><strong>实际上，这两种问题都是管理员权限的问题</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-检查安装\"><a href=\"#4-检查安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.检查安装\"></a>4.检查安装</h2><p>依照<a href=\"https://yishuihean.cn/post/hexo-aurora-github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\">依水何安</a>博客相应步骤验证即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-创建仓库及配置SSH连接\"><a href=\"#5-创建仓库及配置SSH连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.创建仓库及配置SSH连接\"></a>5.创建仓库及配置SSH连接</h2><p>可能是版本问题，我这边不用像<a href=\"https://yishuihean.cn/post/hexo-aurora-github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\">依水何安</a>中间输入y，只要四次回车即可</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>生成的tokens<strong>一定要自己保留下来</strong>，不然之后在github上是看不到</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"6-搭建本地博客\"><a href=\"#6-搭建本地博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.搭建本地博客\"></a>6.搭建本地博客</h2><p>运行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo clean\n$ hexo g\n$ hexo d</code></pre>\n\n<p>等命令时报错，参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/gao5805123\">邪丶魔狱</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"7-上传至本地博客至GitHub\"><a href=\"#7-上传至本地博客至GitHub\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7.上传至本地博客至GitHub\"></a>7.上传至本地博客至GitHub</h2><p>如果使用 <code>hexo d</code> 时，出现 <code>SpawnFailed</code> 的错误:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git config --global user.email &quot;你的邮箱&quot;\ngit config --global user.name &quot;用户名&quot;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"8-安装Aurora主题\"><a href=\"#8-安装Aurora主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8.安装Aurora主题\"></a>8.安装Aurora主题</h2><p>参考<a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/zh/\">Aurora官方文档</a></p>\n<p>布置三色渐变时，大家可以用这个官网找颜色<a href=\"http://www.hepou.com/peise/jianbian.html\">禾坡网</a>，但这个官网无法选择指定数量的渐变，有一定缺陷</p>\n<h2 id=\"9-上传并覆盖GitHub仓库\"><a href=\"#9-上传并覆盖GitHub仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"9.上传并覆盖GitHub仓库\"></a>9.上传并覆盖GitHub仓库</h2><p>如果上传不上，可能有一下原因：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>网络太差，无法连接到github</li>\n<li>配置文件_config.aurora.yml出错，比如用命令行打开把自动缩进也开了，导致一行地址变成两行，造成错误</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"10-图床\"><a href=\"#10-图床\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"10.图床\"></a>10.图床</h2><p>对于一些博客网站来说，从图床引用图片会比直接将图片转码插入文中阅读体验和加载速度都有一个较大的提升。</p>\n<p>用github+PicGo搭建图床：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_39246554\">一念一生～one</a></p>\n<p>有可能会遇到的问题以及解决：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_41692282\">二六</a></p>\n<p><em>我的PicGo里面的相册加载不出来，但外链和github都能用，倒也不是很影响</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"11-博客界面\"><a href=\"#11-博客界面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"11.博客界面\"></a>11.博客界面</h2><p>最后，我搭建的博客页面大概长这样啦：还算是比较成功吧！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fate-zuolun/blog_img@main/202209252013541.png\" alt=\"image-20220925201319228\"></p>\n<p><strong>如有错误，敬请指正，欢迎交流，谢谢♪(･ω･)ﾉ</strong></p>\n<p>​        </p>\n","feature":true,"text":" 搭建方法主要来自于依水何安和Aurora官方文档 提示 由于上面两个文档讲的很详细，左轮这边就不多加赘述了。这边主要是对一些资源以及遇到的一些问题的重新整合。 1.node js的安装及环境配置参考周瑜周 2.安装git参考学为所用和xxkinger 由于学为所用的博客git版...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端技术","slug":"前端技术","count":1,"path":"api/categories/前端技术.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"搭建博客","slug":"搭建博客","count":1,"path":"api/tags/搭建博客.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-node-js%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.node js的安装及环境配置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.安装git</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDhexo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.下载hexo</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.检查安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESSH%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.创建仓库及配置SSH连接</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#6-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6.搭建本地博客</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#7-%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%B3GitHub\"><span class=\"toc-text\">7.上传至本地博客至GitHub</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#8-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Aurora%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">8.安装Aurora主题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#9-%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E5%B9%B6%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96GitHub%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">9.上传并覆盖GitHub仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#10-%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">10.图床</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#11-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">11.博客界面</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zuolun","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/6.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个啥都不会，正在努力学习的小白","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":{"link":"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_51302822?type=blog"},"juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"stack","uid":"1932edd6bc286fe1e67c448fee302e6f","slug":"stack","date":"2022-09-25T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-09-26T16:06:34.794Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/stack.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fate-zuolun/blog_img@main/202209260317660.jpg","text":" 本文主要学习陈小玉老师的《算法训练营》一书 stack容器stack是一个先进后出的容器，比如我们拿一个玻璃瓶装糖果，先下去的糖果往往最后才能拿出来。 stack和vector的不同 vector能对任意位置插入删除，stack只能对栈顶进行操作 vector支持随机访问，st...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C语言","slug":"C语言","count":2,"path":"api/categories/C语言.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":2,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"}],"author":{"name":"zuolun","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/6.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个啥都不会，正在努力学习的小白","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":{"link":"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_51302822?type=blog"},"juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{}}